---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Web Design for Dentists | FisherDigital"
  description="Websites for dental practices across the UK. Help patients find you, book appointments online, and build trust before they walk through the door."
  schemaType="niche"
  niche="Dentists"
  nicheDescription="Professional websites, AI chatbots, and patient booking systems built specifically for dental practices in the UK."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="section-light py-(--spacing-section)">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="label block mb-4">Web design for dentists</span>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-heading font-600 tracking-tight mb-6">
          Patients decide in seconds.<br />
          <span class="text-accent">Make those seconds count.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-light-text-secondary)] max-w-xl mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          A nervous patient Googles "dentist accepting new patients." They scan the top results, look at photos of the practice, check reviews, and book with whoever feels safest. Your website is your waiting room before the waiting room.
        </p>
        <a href="/#contact" data-hover
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-accent text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-sm font-600 hover:bg-accent-hover transition-all shadow-lg shadow-accent/20 hover:shadow-accent/40">
          Book a free call
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pain Points -->
  <section class="bg-white py-(--spacing-section)">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="label block mb-4">The problem</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-600 tracking-tight">
          Why patients pick someone else.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Pain 1 -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--color-border)] p-8 bg-[var(--color-surface-light)]">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-600 mb-3">New patients can't find you</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
            Your practice is excellent. But if someone new to the area searches "NHS dentist near me" or "private dentist [your town]," you're not in the results. Corporate chains with bigger marketing budgets are.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Pain 2 -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--color-border)] p-8 bg-[var(--color-surface-light)]">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-600 mb-3">Phone-only booking loses patients</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
            People want to book at 11pm from their sofa. If the only option is to ring during surgery hours, they'll find a practice that lets them book online. Simple as that.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Pain 3 -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--color-border)] p-8 bg-[var(--color-surface-light)]">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-heading font-600 mb-3">Your website feels clinical, not welcoming</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
            Dental anxiety is real. A cold, outdated website with stock photos of perfect teeth doesn't reassure anyone. Patients want to see your actual team, your practice, and feel like real humans work there.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Build -->
  <section class="section-light py-(--spacing-section)">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <span class="label block mb-4">What you get</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-600 tracking-tight mb-12">
          A website patients actually trust.
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            <div>
              <p class="font-600 text-[var(--color-light-text)] mb-1">Online booking and enquiry forms</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-light-text-secondary)]">Patients pick a treatment type, choose a preferred date, and submit. Your reception team gets a clean request with all the details. No phone tag.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            <div>
              <p class="font-600 text-[var(--color-light-text)] mb-1">Treatment pages with clear pricing</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-light-text-secondary)]">Separate pages for check-ups, cosmetic work, implants, orthodontics, and emergency appointments. Patients see what you offer and what it costs before they pick up the phone.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            <div>
              <p class="font-600 text-[var(--color-light-text)] mb-1">Google Reviews pulled onto your site</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-light-text-secondary)]">Real patient reviews displayed directly on your website. Social proof from people who've actually sat in your chair. Nothing builds trust faster.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            <div>
              <p class="font-600 text-[var(--color-light-text)] mb-1">AI chatbot for after-hours patient queries</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-light-text-secondary)]">On the Professional plan, a chatbot answers common questions at any hour. "Do you accept new NHS patients?" "How much are veneers?" "Can I book an emergency appointment?" Handled instantly.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-white py-(--spacing-section)">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-600 tracking-tight mb-6">
        We already built one. Come see it.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10">
        Bright Smile Dental is a demo site we built to show what's possible. Real structure, real content, ready to adapt for your practice.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-5">
        <a href="/demos/bright-smile-dental/" data-hover
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-accent text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-sm font-600 hover:bg-accent-hover transition-all shadow-lg shadow-accent/20 hover:shadow-accent/40">
          See a live demo
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/#contact" data-hover
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-sm font-500 border border-[var(--color-border-light)] hover:border-accent hover:text-accent transition-all">
          Book a free call
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
